    <body>
        <div class="page-content">
            <hgroup>
                <h1>The Wedding</h1>
                <h3>Silewski-Osborn Wedding</h3>
            </hgroup>


            <p>Family and friends,</p>
            
            <p>Welcome to our wedding website! We are so excited to announce our engagement and feel blessed in share our day, 
            May 10, 2013 with you! We look forward to seeing you all and hope you find this website helpful as your plan your 
            day with us!</p>

            <p>Love, Holly & Matthew</p>

            <hr />

            <hgroup>
                <h2>The Proposal</h2>
                <h3>How it Went Down</h3>
            </hgroup>

            <ol id="timeline">
                <li>
                    <h4><time>5:00</time></h4>
                    <span>Fake dinner plans with Jim and Ling Ling.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h4><time>5:30</time></h4>
                    <span>Matthew arrives at the house, with a <a href="http://www.bmclimo.com/">limo</a>, to pick up Holly.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h4><time>6:00</time></h4>
                    <span>Private scenic <a href="http://www.kenmoreair.com/">seaplane tour</a> of the city that brought them together.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h4><time>7:00</time></h4>
                    <span>Private dining at Canlis, on Lake Union, in the <a href="http://www.canlis.com/dining/about_cache.aspx">Caché room</a>.</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <h4><time>8:00</time></h4>
                    <span>Matthew pops the question and Holly says yes.</span>
                </li>
            </ol>

            <div id="gallery">

                <figure id="mainImage">
                    <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-1.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" />
                    <figcaption>The &quot;Rock&quot;, I cannot take credit for picking it out Holly gave me a limited set of choices.</figcaption>
                </figure>

                <ul id="images">
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-1.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-1.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="The &quot;Rock&quot;, I cannot take credit for picking it out Holly gave me a limited set of choices." class="selected" />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-2.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-2.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="Declaimer: This is not the real proposal, neither of us was this calm during the real deal!" />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-3.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-3.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="The sealed deal after holly said yes!" />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="last">
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-4.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-4.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="All said and done, during this picture Holly asked me what I had said to her when I proposed." />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-5.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-5.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="The two of us waiting on our pilot at the Kenmore seaport, the clouds parted just in time to give us an amazing view." />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-6.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-6.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="Hanging out in the back of our plane after we landed, it is very cozy back there." />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-7.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-7.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="View from the Caché room, it overlooks Lake Union and Gasworks Park." />
