                    </li>
                    <li class="last">
                         <a href="@Href("~/images/proposal-8.jpg")">
                            <img src="@Href("~/images/proposal-8.jpg")" alt="The Proposal" title="One of our desert plates, yes we had more than one, with congratulations from the Canlis Staff." />
                        </a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>I, Matthew, would like to take a moment to say thank you to all the people that helped make this proposal a 
            night to remember. Brad Wilson, for all your support and help planning, executing, and most importantly, not 
            talking me out of it. Jim Wang, for taking the awesome pictures you see above. Jeff Wilcox, for providing so 
            many great suggestions and providing support. Ben Pham, for providing the awesome design of this site. Most 
            important of all I would like to thank Mr. Silewski for giving Holly and I his blessing.</p>


        </div>
        <script src="@Href("~/Scripts/jquery-1.7.2.min.js")"></script>
        <script>
            $(function() {
                var myFullText = "";

                $.each($('h3'), function() {
                    $(this).addClass('line');
                    myFullText = '<span>' + $(this).text() + '</span>';
                    $(this).html(myFullText);
                });


                $('#images img').click(function() {
                    var image = $("#mainImage img");
                    $('.selected').removeClass('selected');
                    image.attr('src', $(this).attr("src"));
                    $("#mainImage figcaption").text($(this).attr("title"));
                    $(this).addClass('selected');
                    return false;
                });

                $('#mainImage img').hover(function() {
                    $('#mainImage figcaption').slideToggle('fast');
                });

            });
        </script>
    </body>
</html>